OL,3,C'My dad didn't hug myself or kiss my
OL,4,Cmum,' says son of infected blood victim
OL,6,FITV Border reporter Isla Todd spoke to
OL,7,Fthe Strachan family about the impact
OL,8,Fthe infected blood scandal has had on
OL,9,Ftheir lives
OL,11,FThe father of a man who died of HIV
OL,12,Fdue to the infected blood scandal
OL,13,Fwould not hug or kiss his son or wife
OL,14,Fbefore he passed away for fear of
OL,15,Fspreading the virus.
OL,17,FJohn Strachan died in 1987, just two
OL,18,Fweeks before his son's ninth birthday.
OL,19,FHe had contracted HIV in the early
OL,20,F1980s from an infected blood
OL,21,Ftransfusion.
