OL,3,C'My dad didn't hug myself or kiss my
OL,4,Cmum,' says son of infected blood victim
OL,6,FHis son Bob Strachan told ITV Border:
OL,7,F"My dad didn't hug myself or even kiss
OL,8,Fmy mum because he didn't know how this
OL,9,Fwas passed on.
OL,11,F"My mum had told me that he died of
OL,12,Fkidney failure. And that was what I
OL,13,Fbelieved until my teens."
OL,15,FBob said his mother then sat him down
OL,16,Fand told him the real story.
