OL,6,FThe family were so affected by the
OL,7,Fstigma of HIV, at a time when little
OL,8,Fwas known about the infection, that
OL,9,Fthey moved from Peterhead to New
OL,10,FZealand, then Canada, before returning
OL,11,Fto Scotland.
OL,13,F"There was a lot of ignorance around
OL,14,Fit (HIV), so it's just really hard to
OL,15,Fthink about, something that was life
OL,16,Fchanging and life ending, not just for
OL,17,Fthat person, but for everyone around
OL,18,Fthem," Bob said.
