OL,6,F"It's the condition of life leading up
OL,7,Fto that. It's dealing with our mental
OL,8,Fhealth after this and throughout all
OL,9,Fof our lives."
OL,11,FWhat is the infected blood inquiry?
OL,13,F30,000 people were infected with
OL,14,Fcontaminated blood in the 1970s and
OL,15,F1980s. A public inquiry into the
OL,16,Fscandal will report its findings on
OL,17,FMonday 20 May.
