OL,6,FThe people impacted included those who
OL,7,Fneeded blood transfusions for
OL,8,Faccidents, in surgery, or during
OL,9,Fchildbirth, and patients with certain
OL,10,Fblood disorders who were treated with
OL,11,Fdonated blood plasma products, or
OL,12,Fblood transfusions.
OL,14,FThe inquiry concluded today (Monday 20
OL,15,FMay 2024), finding that the thousands
OL,16,Fof lives impacted was "no accident".
