OL,3,C'My dad didn't hug myself or kiss my
OL,4,Cmum,' says son of infected blood victim
OL,6,FHe continued: "First and foremost,
OL,7,Fthere has to be an admission of guilt
OL,8,Fand apology made.
OL,10,F"You know, obviously they can't make
OL,11,Frestitution for the lives that have
OL,12,Fbeen lost or things like that. But
OL,13,Fthere has to be accountability, first
OL,14,Fand foremost is the bare minimum.
OL,16,F"I would certainly like to see
OL,17,Frecompense of loss of earnings at the
OL,18,Fminimum for those people that did
OL,19,Fthat. But also, then we have to take
OL,20,Finto consideration inheritance that
OL,21,Fcould have been left."
