OL,3,C'My dad didn't hug myself or kiss my
OL,4,Cmum,' says son of infected blood victim
OL,6,FBob's daughter, Bobbi Strachan, never
OL,7,Fhad the chance to meet her
OL,8,Fgrandfather, but has still been
OL,9,Fimpacted by this part of their family
OL,10,Fhistory.
OL,12,FShe told ITV Border: "I would get
OL,13,Freally emotional and I would talk
OL,14,Fabout certain things because grandad
OL,15,Fsounded like such an amazing person,
OL,16,Fand I would have loved to have got to
OL,17,Fknow him.
OL,19,F"I'm 22 years old and this has been
OL,20,Fgoing on double my life - 40 years -
OL,21,Fand it caused a lot of issues.
